{"word":"G2872 - κοπιάω - kopiáō - kop-ee-ah'-o - Labour","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κοπιάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kopiáō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kop-ee-ah'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Labour"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உழை, வறுத்தப்பட்டு பாரஞ்சுமை, பிரயாசப்படு, இளைப்படை, பாடுபடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to grow weary, tired, exhausted,"},{"paragraph":"2. to labor with wearisome effort, to toil"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2873 - κόπος - kópos - kop'-os/2873\">G2873</a>; to <i>feel fatigue</i>; by implication to <i>work hard:</i> - (bestow) labour, toil, be wearied."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2872 - κοπιάω - kopiáō - kop-ee-ah'-o/2872\">G2872</a>, <a href=\"#/G2873 - κόπος - kópos - kop'-os/2873\">G2873</a>"}]}